N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 103.12 - Vehicle and Traffic Law

State Regulations

Except for those sections which are inconsistent with or
modified by the sections of this Part, the provisions of the Vehicle and

Traffic Law of the State of New York shall apply. Notes
